{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CmJxYRpJBbyj1cJhNqnGtQ","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. I now have all three files. Let me present the complete contents in a well-organized format:\n\n---\n\n## File 1: Frontend Types (`sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/types.ts`)\n\n**Bet and Phase Types:**\n- `BetSide`: \"green\" | \"red\"\n- `RoundPhase`: \"betting\" | \"locked\" | \"resolving\" | \"complete\"\n- `CandleOutcome`: \"green\" | \"red\" | \"doji\"\n\n**Candle (OHLC) Data:**\n```typescript\ninterface Candle {\n  open: number;\n  high: number;\n  low: number;\n  close: number;\n  openTime: number;  // Unix timestamp ms\n  closeTime: number; // Unix timestamp ms\n}\n```\n\n**Player Bet:**\n```typescript\ninterface PlayerBet {\n  address: string;\n  side: BetSide;\n  amount: number;     // in $\n  timestamp: number;\n  displayName?: string;\n}\n```\n\n**Pool State:**\n```typescript\ninterface PoolState {\n  greenPool: number;\n  redPool: number;\n  totalPool: number;\n  playerCount: number;\n  greenBets: PlayerBet[];\n  redBets: PlayerBet[];\n}\n```\n\n**Complete Round:**\n```typescript\ninterface Round {\n  id: string;\n  phase: RoundPhase;\n  pool: PoolState;\n  createdAt: number;\n  bettingEndsAt: number;\n  resolvedAt?: number;\n  targetCandleTime: number;\n  outcome?: CandleOutcome;\n  resultCandle?: Candle;\n  carryoverAmount: number;\n  seedHash: string;\n  serverSeed?: string;\n  blockHash?: string;\n  winners?: string[];\n  payouts?: Record<string, number>;\n  payoutAmount?: number;\n}\n```\n\n**User History:**\n```typescript\ninterface UserRoundHistory {\n  round: Round;\n  userBet: PlayerBet;\n  payout: number;\n  won: boolean;\n}\n```\n\n**Context Value (main state interface):**\n```typescript\ninterface CloseCallContextValue {\n  // Round state\n  currentRound: Round | null;\n  completedRound: Round | null;\n  recentCandles: Candle[];\n  currentPrice: number;\n  candleProgress: number;\n  userHistory: UserRoundHistory[];\n  carryoverJackpot: number;\n\n  // User bet state\n  pendingAmount: number;\n  pendingSide: BetSide | null;\n  userBet: PlayerBet | null;\n\n  // Loading states\n  loading: boolean;\n  placingBet: boolean;\n  claiming: boolean;\n\n  // Actions\n  setPendingAmount: (amount: number) => void;\n  setPendingSide: (side: BetSide | null) => void;\n  placeBet: (side?: BetSide) => Promise<void>;\n  adjustBetAmount: (adjustment: \"half\" | \"double\" | \"max\") => void;\n  claimPayout: () => Promise<void>;\n  clearCompletedRound: () => void;\n\n  // Computed\n  potentialPayout: number;\n  userOdds: number;\n\n  // Utils\n  refreshRound: () => void;\n}\n```\n\n**Constants:**\n- `DEFAULT_BET_AMOUNT = 0.5`\n- `MIN_BET_AMOUNT = 0.1`\n- `MAX_BET_AMOUNT = 1000`\n- `PLATFORM_FEE_BPS = 300` (3%)\n- `PLATFORM_FEE = 0.03`\n- `DOJI_THRESHOLD_BPS = 1` (0.01%)\n- `CANDLE_SPEED_MULTIPLIER = 1`\n- `CANDLE_DURATION_MS = 60000` (60 seconds)\n- `BETTING_WINDOW_MS = 10000` (10 seconds)\n- `SIDE_COLORS = { green: \"#45b058\", red: \"#dc3545\", doji: \"#f0b820\" }`\n\n---\n\n## File 2: Frontend Context (`sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/context/CloseCallContext.tsx`)\n\n**Default Context Value:** Initializes all fields with null/false/0 defaults and empty function stubs.\n\n**Provider State (useState hooks):**\n- `currentRound: Round | null`\n- `completedRound: Round | null`\n- `recentCandles: Candle[]`\n- `currentPrice: number`\n- `candleProgress: number`\n- `carryoverJackpot: number`\n- `userHistory: UserRoundHistory[]`\n- `pendingAmount: number` (default: DEFAULT_BET_AMOUNT)\n- `pendingSide: BetSide | null`\n- `loading: boolean`\n- `placingBet: boolean`\n- `claiming: boolean`\n\n**Computed Values (useMemo):**\n- `userBet`: Finds user's bet in `currentRound.pool.greenBets` or `.redBets` by address\n- `potentialPayout`: Calculated from user's bet or pending selection using `calculatePotentialPayout()`\n- `userOdds`: User's share of winning pool as percentage\n\n**Key Actions:**\n- `placeBet(sideOverride?)`: Takes optional side override, validates min/max amounts, checks balance, calls `mockPlaceBet()`\n- `adjustBetAmount(\"half\" | \"double\" | \"max\")`: Adjusts pending amount with min/max clamping\n- `refreshRound()`: Updates `currentRound` and `recentCandles` from mock\n- `claimPayout()`: Validates winner status, simulates 1s delay, clears `completedRound`\n- `clearCompletedRound()`: Resets `completedRound` state\n\n**Subscriptions & Polling:**\n- Subscribes to `subscribeToRound()` for round updates\n- Subscribes to `subscribeToCompletedRound()` for result display\n- Polls every 100ms to update `candleProgress` and interpolate `currentPrice`\n- Price interpolation uses bullish/bearish logic based on open vs close\n\n**History Update:** Watches `address` and `currentRound.phase` to fetch and sort user history\n\n---\n\n## File 3: On-Chain State (`sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/state.rs`)\n\n**Rust Enums (all derive AnchorSerialize, AnchorDeserialize, Clone, Copy, Debug, InitSpace):**\n\n```rust\npub enum BetSide {\n    Green,\n    Red,\n}\n\npub enum CloseCallPhase {\n    Open,      // Round is open for bets (first 30s of candle)\n    Settled,   // Outcome determined, payouts distributed\n    Refunded,  // All bets refunded (invalid, timeout, or force close)\n}\n\npub enum Outcome {\n    Pending,\n    Green,\n    Red,\n    Refund,\n}\n```\n\n**Bet Entry:**\n```rust\npub struct BetEntry {\n    pub player: Pubkey,\n    pub amount_lamports: u64,\n}\n```\n\n**Global Config (PDA: `[\"closecall_config\"]`):**\n```rust\npub struct CloseCallConfig {\n    pub authority: Pubkey,\n    pub treasury: Pubkey,\n    pub pyth_feed_id: [u8; 32],          // BTC/USD feed ID\n    pub betting_window_secs: u32,         // default 30\n    pub max_entries_per_side: u8,         // default 32\n    pub paused: bool,\n    pub bump: u8,\n}\n```\n\n**Close Call Round (PDA: `[\"cc_round\", &round_id]`):**\n```rust\npub struct CloseCallRound {\n    pub round_id: [u8; 8],                // Backend-generated, used in PDA seeds\n    pub server: Pubkey,                   // Server wallet that paid rent & settles\n    pub phase: CloseCallPhase,\n\n    #[max_len(32)]\n    pub green_entries: Vec<BetEntry>,\n    #[max_len(32)]\n    pub red_entries: Vec<BetEntry>,\n    pub green_pool: u64,\n    pub red_pool: u64,\n\n    pub open_price: i64,                  // Pyth price (scaled integer)\n    pub open_price_expo: i32,             // Pyth exponent\n    pub close_price: i64,                 // 0 until settled\n\n    pub created_at: i64,                  // Unix timestamp\n    pub betting_ends_at: i64,             // Unix timestamp\n    pub resolve_deadline: i64,            // Timeout deadline\n\n    pub outcome: Outcome,\n    pub total_fee: u64,\n    pub bump: u8,\n}\n```\n\n**Event:**\n```rust\npub struct RoundSettled {\n    pub round_id: [u8; 8],\n    pub outcome: Outcome,\n    pub open_price: i64,\n    pub close_price: i64,\n    pub green_pool: u64,\n    pub red_pool: u64,\n    pub total_fee: u64,\n    pub num_winners: u8,\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Key Observations Across All Three Files\n\n1. **Frontend uses **dollar amounts** (`PlayerBet.amount: number` is in $), on-chain uses **lamports** (`BetEntry.amount_lamports: u64`)\n2. **Frontend phase names** (betting/locked/resolving/complete) differ from **on-chain phase names** (Open/Settled/Refunded)\n3. **Frontend outcome** uses strings (green/red/doji), **on-chain outcome** is a Rust enum (Green/Red/Refund/Pending)\n4. **On-chain supports max 32 entries per side**, frontend has no documented hard limit\n5. **Pyth price is stored as i64 with exponent** on-chain; frontend interpolates prices during round progression\n6. **Config betting window: 30 seconds** on-chain, but **frontend constants show 10s** (BETTING_WINDOW_MS = 10000)\n7. **candle_progress** (0.0 to 1.0) drives price interpolation with 3-phase logic (bullish/bearish branches)"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a7566a9781dd2a372 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 42045\ntool_uses: 4\nduration_ms: 29205</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d3481bfc-609c-41f4-8bb8-2d2167df8050","uuid":"20088ae5-994b-4278-ab03-15278ef28031","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find and read the following files thoroughly:\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/types.ts` \n2. Any context file in `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/context/` (CloseCallContext.tsx or similar)\n3. `sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/state.rs` (on-chain state definitions)\n\nFor each file, report the FULL contents. I need to see every type, constant, enum value, and field.","agentId":"a7566a9781dd2a372","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. I now have all three files. Let me present the complete contents in a well-organized format:\n\n---\n\n## File 1: Frontend Types (`sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/types.ts`)\n\n**Bet and Phase Types:**\n- `BetSide`: \"green\" | \"red\"\n- `RoundPhase`: \"betting\" | \"locked\" | \"resolving\" | \"complete\"\n- `CandleOutcome`: \"green\" | \"red\" | \"doji\"\n\n**Candle (OHLC) Data:**\n```typescript\ninterface Candle {\n  open: number;\n  high: number;\n  low: number;\n  close: number;\n  openTime: number;  // Unix timestamp ms\n  closeTime: number; // Unix timestamp ms\n}\n```\n\n**Player Bet:**\n```typescript\ninterface PlayerBet {\n  address: string;\n  side: BetSide;\n  amount: number;     // in $\n  timestamp: number;\n  displayName?: string;\n}\n```\n\n**Pool State:**\n```typescript\ninterface PoolState {\n  greenPool: number;\n  redPool: number;\n  totalPool: number;\n  playerCount: number;\n  greenBets: PlayerBet[];\n  redBets: PlayerBet[];\n}\n```\n\n**Complete Round:**\n```typescript\ninterface Round {\n  id: string;\n  phase: RoundPhase;\n  pool: 