{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_015FePqh2Nw48QA1BPmtWYyA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01YbMC83TRwEMLBJtdJ1vUJN","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/100-close-call/spec.md","old_string":"- [ ] [frontend] Update `features/close-call/types.ts`: remove DOJI threshold, carryover, commit-reveal fields (`seedHash`, `serverSeed`, `blockHash`, `carryoverAmount`). Remove `claimPayout` from context actions (auto-payout). Fix constants: `BETTING_WINDOW_MS = 30000` (was 10000), `MIN_BET_AMOUNT` to 0.001 SOL, `MAX_BET_AMOUNT` to 100 SOL. Align `RoundPhase` with on-chain `CloseCallPhase` (Open/Settled/Refunded). Align `CandleOutcome` — remove \"doji\", add \"refund\". Update `PoolState` to match on-chain `green_pool`/`red_pool` fields. Run `pnpm lint` to confirm no type errors cascade.","new_string":"- [x] [frontend] Update `features/close-call/types.ts`: remove DOJI threshold, carryover, commit-reveal fields (`seedHash`, `serverSeed`, `blockHash`, `carryoverAmount`). Remove `claimPayout` from context actions (auto-payout). Fix constants: `BETTING_WINDOW_MS = 30000` (was 10000), `MIN_BET_AMOUNT` to 0.001 SOL, `MAX_BET_AMOUNT` to 100 SOL. Align `RoundPhase` with on-chain `CloseCallPhase` (Open/Settled/Refunded). Align `CandleOutcome` — remove \"doji\", add \"refund\". Update `PoolState` to match on-chain `green_pool`/`red_pool` fields. Run `pnpm lint` to confirm no type errors cascade. (done: iteration 30)"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":432,"cache_read_input_tokens":102973,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":432},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d3481bfc-609c-41f4-8bb8-2d2167df8050","uuid":"48281bef-47b